						"vec3 dirHalfVector = normalize( dirVector + viewPosition );",
						"float dirDotNormalHalf = max( dot( normal, dirHalfVector ), 0.0 );",
						"float dirSpecularWeight = specularTex.r * max( pow( dirDotNormalHalf, uShininess ), 0.0 );",

