	// 	based on SpiderGL shadow map example
	// 		http://spidergl.org/example.php?id=6
	// 	originally from
	//		http://www.gamedev.net/topic/442138-packing-a-float-into-a-a8r8g8b8-texture-shader/page__whichpage__1%25EF%25BF%25BD
